title: This is nuts!
comment: You know when you've over did something when the ui is better than on the original. This is so far the best emulator for PSP I've ever seen. Even thou PSP games are quite demanding on hardware you can run 30% games on any android, and 90% on hi-end android device. (and no the god of war was laggy on PSP already so I don't count that in). The software it self handles the emulation quite nicely. From my personal experience It's quite hard to create a working emulator, but to optimize it this well, I'm not sure if I would be able to do that. If you are into PSP games this is an emulator for you, Or perhaps you're just tiered of angry birds and other android games and you want to play something better on the go this is an emulator for you.
